        - Report Info: Exception Handling (rejections). Goal: Organize. Viz: Accordion component (HTML/CSS/JS). Interaction: Click to expand/collapse. Justification: Neatly organizes dense information about multiple error scenarios, preventing UI clutter and improving readability.
